{"tid":1223913,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"司機涉開車撞警員　警方強調情況危險開兩槍是別無他法","createTime":"2019-06-14T23:46:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-15T01:43:08.000Z","uid":53003,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"ca72b89964acc8b7449291e2a299a0da03994864","tid":1223913,"uid":53003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T23:46:23.000Z","msg":"警方在元朗西鐵站附近截查車輛時，一名司機涉嫌開車逃走，並企圖撞向警員，警員開了兩槍。<br />\n<br />\n警方其後在錦繡花園迴旋處，找到涉案私家車，司機不知所蹤。警方拘捕私家車女乘客及車主，正通緝涉案司機。警方說事發時情況非常危險，私家車直衝向警員，警員感到生命受威脅，強調開槍是別無他法。<br />\n<br />\n事發在凌晨一時許，警方說在元朗西鐵站對開的士站，截查一輛懷疑違反交通規例的私家車時，司機開車企圖撞向警員，警員連開兩槍制止，司機駕車逃去。警方其後找到涉案私家車，司機不知所蹤，駕駛席有血漬，一邊車窗粉碎。<br />\n[url]<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1462980-20190615.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1462980-20190615.htm&d=YB8lrFeyQ%2BkzHCEHpdql8BZ9qy%2BOiqBAJcOKDokr%2FlY%3D&h=24ca6051\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1462980-20190615.htm&h=8ce2bed5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1462980-20190615.htm</a><br />\n[/url]"},{"pid":"1df86106db8f0d8180936de952cf07472a3fca2c","tid":1223913,"uid":68151,"like":28,"dislike":1,"score":27,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T23:49:38.000Z","msg":"依家開槍好基本"},{"pid":"ef2da9836c89570f9ca3fd5d070f58c60ce03d6c","tid":1223913,"uid":108337,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T23:50:33.000Z","msg":"開槍當食生菜"},{"pid":"22659990fba5bf9eb1466d8582c4840f83bd1904","tid":1223913,"uid":173271,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T23:51:17.000Z","msg":"記者都成黑影<br />\n開槍別無他法"},{"pid":"01f4829c053bd6b10ab7fffed9f2129fedbe4f57","tid":1223913,"uid":80567,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T23:51:51.000Z","msg":"狗講咩都唔好信到十足十"},{"pid":"1f927f586744c280f23d2a76229ac18840669251","tid":1223913,"uid":212336,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T23:52:41.000Z","msg":"以後行街呼吸都係企圖殺警"},{"pid":"e6cfe0753682ff729bc6793bdbcc8c4c2f9af948","tid":1223913,"uid":126256,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T23:57:17.000Z","msg":"以前我可能會信<br />\n而家就......<br />\n狼來了呢個道理小朋友都識<br />\n點解警察咁大個人都唔識"},{"pid":"72091422371ccacc8b263189c1f4c192e499dc8c","tid":1223913,"uid":79075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T00:01:16.000Z","msg":"哈"},{"pid":"95b48f0079a5ba835803c0013e1dc74295347054","tid":1223913,"uid":79075,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"72091422371ccacc8b263189c1f4c192e499dc8c","tid":1223913,"uid":79075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T00:01:16.000Z","msg":"哈"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T00:01:32.000Z","msg":"開槍？屌你老母臭閪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f81603db4a9b0d840ba7944ae88a26d4045b58b7","tid":1223913,"uid":4330,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T01:28:40.000Z","msg":"呢類事件只會有增無減<br />\n班狗已經慣左手勢 <br />\n係咪都開左槍先<br />\n<br />\n麻煩d傻仔唔好再合理化開槍事件"},{"pid":"bc9c54d86908cac87c4284f4a58684abb081f1c5","tid":1223913,"uid":89834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T01:30:38.000Z","msg":"幾撚準 咁都射得中"},{"pid":"9c4d2c5f4c5196c098dcb58a5cc2dde500a50382","tid":1223913,"uid":25468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T01:38:08.000Z","msg":"其實有車衝埋黎，要開槍射邊個位先可以令車即刻停低同令司機踩唔到油？"},{"pid":"c583b6d7b099c13aef5bc3c8cef3a61ffbbe6e74","tid":1223913,"uid":224857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9c4d2c5f4c5196c098dcb58a5cc2dde500a50382","tid":1223913,"uid":25468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T01:38:08.000Z","msg":"其實有車衝埋黎，要開槍射邊個位先可以令車即刻停低同令司機踩唔到油？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T01:41:18.000Z","msg":"有生命危險唔避仲開槍,司機腳在油門死左都係油門會唔會撞到呢"},{"pid":"95fc01964f56878d8610515be1f2a788865c228f","tid":1223913,"uid":245409